node.text: Every generation has its hero. #WBPartner. Interrupting my Instagram break to share about an important film. Discover Bryan Stevenson’s remarkable story in @justmercyfilm. Catch it early in LA and NYC on Christmas and everywhere January 10! And let’s continue to have the important conversations about criminal justice reform and speak out/stand up for those who’s voices might not be heard.  @eji_org #justmercy

#SchmidtsPartner I think we can all agree that the holiday season usually brings about a lot of stress and anxiety! For me, I try my best to stay present in each day and not think of any and all the things that could go wrong. But I also make sure I'm wearing a good deodorant as my armpits are usually on high alert during the holiday season, aka the BO is strong! I discovered @schmidtsnaturals a few years back and it has made a big difference in my life. I love that Schmidt’s is a company that makes products that are not only safe for us to use, make us feel good while using them, and they are also mindful of the planet. Hopefully with their new Sage + Vetiver deodorant made from hemp seed oil, it will help me sage away any negative energy that tries to come about. If not, at least I'll smell good and you can too by using the code: FEMALECOLLECTIVE to get free US shipping!

I’m not telling anyone to deny their pain. Acknowledge that it happened, but also know that you grew from it. At least personally I know that I grew from all the pain I’ve dealt with. It sucks that I had to go through certain things, but from that I grew into the person that I am today and I love the person that I am becoming. 
xo, @candacereels
